headline: L3Harris Sets Date for Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Release
summary: MELBOURNE, Fla., December 30, 2025--L3Harris Technologies (NYSE: LHX) will release its fourth quarter 2025 financial results before the market opens on Thursday, Jan. 29, 2026.

headline: L3Harris Technologies’ Q4 2025 Earnings: What to Expect
summary: L3Harris Technologies will release its fourth-quarter earnings soon, and analysts anticipate a double-digit profit dip.
